snippet.title: Boxing Match - Interton #18
snippet.description: Just a quick look at Boxing Match for Interton VC 4000. The game starts with an obvious rip of "Gonna Fly Now" by Bill Conti. The game itself is a digitized version of Rock 'em Sock 'em. Easy controls and only two player gameplay. Blogpost: http://retro-spill.blogspot.com/2013/04/18-boxing-match-vc-4000.html
